"Heart Me"

When Raven's friend, Tracey (Lyndon
Smith), is fired, evicted and her bank
accounts emptied as a result of being
hacked by a man she met on a dating app,
Raven helps to locate the culprit.
However, Raven asks for her team's help
when the hacker is found dead and Tracy
wakes up in a motel room with the murder
weapon and no memory of what happened.
